About this item

Product details

❤ Hello, Dear Customer, (ლ╹◡╹ლ) Welcome to ☛ HONGLONG ☚ Store !

 

HONGLONG backpack purse for women is made with close attention, wear it as a backpack or convert it to a crossbody or shoulder bag. The tubular top handle and back slide pocket make it easy to grab and carry your bag. The strap length of the backpack can be easily adjusted so that it is suitable for people of different heights. This PU leather backpack is lightweight and stylish which is perfect for work, college, business or everyday use.

Color: Black

Material: PU Leather

Feature: Large capacity, Multifunction, Secure rear zipper design

Age Rang: Adult

Care: Wipe clean

Closure: Top zip-around closure

Handle Type: Adjustable shoulder straps; top handle

Exterior Details: 1 main compartment with an interior pocket, 2 interior slit pockets, 2 side pockets, and 1 front pocket with smooth zippers; brushed metal hardware

Interior Details: 1 back zipper pocket

Applicable occasions: work, shopping, travel, gift giving gifts

  • ✿ Multi-functional Compartments: 1 main compartment with an interior pocket, 2 interior slit pockets, 2 side pockets, 1 front pocket with smooth zippers, 1 back zipper pocket
